column2: Give MavenImporters a chance to set user properties.

column3:
Subclasses of MavenImporter can override customizeUserProperties().
Improved robustness of maven 2/maven 3 switching in MiscImportingTest.
Fixes IDEA-123761 MavenImporters should be able to set properties for import

Hi Christian, I'm sorry for such a long silence. I've looked at the change and found it useful. It's a pity that it was not merged back in 2014 year. I've merged it with the current master branch using the following commit: 9fc5d9d
Thanks for the contribution!
Give MavenImporters a chance to set user properties.
